ng -v to check version of angular cli

To generate module
ng g module [module-name] --routing 

ng new application 
ng new application --routing 


To host angular application on angular sever
ng s --host IP Address
ng s --host 10.18.80.143 

npm install @angular/cli -g

ng build --prod
ng s -o to open server on browser
npm config  --to set proxy related 
npm help
ng g c componene_name -it ----to generate component with inline template

